{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/urban-aboriginal-ministry/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ffeb34ba-35fa-56e4-a2ce-9d81868b65a4","html":"<p>The  Urban Aboriginal Ministry is a ministry of the Anglican Parish of St. Mary Magdalene in the Greater Vancouver Area to the First Nations people and their loved ones. The Ministry provide medicine wheel circles with smudging for all occasions (on request) and cultural funerals and weddings. It hosts Annual Feasts on Christmas, Easter and Thanksgiving. They also provide cultural gatherings where they teach arts &#x26; crafts such as drum making to restore the traditional ancestral teachings. The UAM responds to calls for practical needs such as food, furniture, clothing and transportation.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#digital-outreach\">Digital Outreach</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#executive-advisory-board-functions\">Executive Advisory Board Functions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sumdging-ceremony\">Smudging Ceremony</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#winter-feast\">Winter Feast</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"digital-outreach\"><a href=\"#digital-outreach\" aria-label=\"digital outreach permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Digital Outreach</h2>\n<p>My principal role as the digital communications officer is to build and maintain the new website.\nIt has been set up on Bluehost for now and runs on a wordpress blog.  The site is a collective\nproject. Images and videos are gathered by myself and others and posted by myself.  We are looking for content moderators.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://urbanaboriginalministry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Urban Aboriginal Ministry Site</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"executive-advisory-board-functions\"><a href=\"#executive-advisory-board-functions\" aria-label=\"executive advisory board functions permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Executive Advisory Board Functions</h2>\n<p>We meet as an advisory board and review all of the activities of the ministry once per month.\nI report on my role as the website administrator and provide back up for other board members.</p>\n<h2 id=\"smudging-ceremony\"><a href=\"#smudging-ceremony\" aria-label=\"smudging ceremony permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Smudging Ceremony</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 600px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsbylumen/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/82472/mainbanner.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/gatsbylumen/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/01472/mainbanner.webp 240w,\n/gatsbylumen/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/222bd/mainbanner.webp 480w,\n/gatsbylumen/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/965c5/mainbanner.webp 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/gatsbylumen/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/3bc27/mainbanner.jpg 240w,\n/gatsbylumen/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/98431/mainbanner.jpg 480w,\n/gatsbylumen/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/82472/mainbanner.jpg 600w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/gatsbylumen/static/88bb62809a91d62e13d6606243256147/82472/mainbanner.jpg\"\n          alt=\"mainbanner.jpg\"\n          title=\"mainbanner.jpg\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"winter-feast\"><a href=\"#winter-feast\" aria-label=\"winter feast permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Winter Feast</h2>\n<p>Friday, November 22nd from 6-9:00 pm</p>\n<p>At St. Mary Magdalene\n2950 Laurel Street at West 14th Avenue\nVancouver, BC</p>\n<p>At this fundraising event for the UAM, everyone, indigenous and settler alike, share in a feast that features traditional food such as moose stew and bannock. A silent auction offers something for everyone, from cozy woollen Cowichan handknitting to beautiful hand carved silver bracelets.</p>\n<p>Tickets are $20.00 and are available from the Reverend  Vivian Seegers, e-mail: vivianseegers@hotmail.com or call 604-816-3348</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 612px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsbylumen/static/d5d2f416243ad5e2d409fe4c5d29de00/a3506/winterfestposter2019.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 129.41176470588235%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/gatsbylumen/static/d5d2f416243ad5e2d409fe4c5d29de00/01472/winterfestposter2019.webp 240w,\n/gatsbylumen/static/d5d2f416243ad5e2d409fe4c5d29de00/222bd/winterfestposter2019.webp 480w,\n/gatsbylumen/static/d5d2f416243ad5e2d409fe4c5d29de00/09766/winterfestposter2019.webp 612w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/gatsbylumen/static/d5d2f416243ad5e2d409fe4c5d29de00/3bc27/winterfestposter2019.jpg 240w,\n/gatsbylumen/static/d5d2f416243ad5e2d409fe4c5d29de00/98431/winterfestposter2019.jpg 480w,\n/gatsbylumen/static/d5d2f416243ad5e2d409fe4c5d29de00/a3506/winterfestposter2019.jpg 612w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/gatsbylumen/static/d5d2f416243ad5e2d409fe4c5d29de00/a3506/winterfestposter2019.jpg\"\n          alt=\"winterfeast\"\n          title=\"winterfeast\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/urban-aboriginal-ministry/","tagSlugs":["/tag/design/","/tag/typography/","/tag/web-development/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-11-07T22:40:32.169Z","description":" The Urban Aboriginal Ministry is a ministry of St. Mary Magdelene Anglican Church and supports Prayer Circles, Four Annual Feasts: Easter, Thanksgiving, Winterfest, and Christmas, Traditional as well as Ceremonies and Pastoral Care.","tags":["Design","Typography","Web Development"],"title":"Urban Aboriginal Ministry","socialImage":"/media/mainbanner.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/urban-aboriginal-ministry/"}}}